original_title: Lesbian Adventures: Older Women, Younger Girls 14
overview: Beautiful older women continue to seduce gorgeous young girls in the 14th volume of Lesbian Adventures Older Women, Younger Girls. Cute blonde Kenna James is a terrible personal assistant. Her boss Cory Chase gives her many chances to improve, but this one will be the last. Kenna gives everything she's got to keep her job. The stunning Vina Sky meets her therapist, Dani Jensen, for her weekly session. This time her shrink suggests an unorthodox approach to her problem. Finally, Sami and Joey (Liv Wild) are twins, but Sami is living a double life. She's in a relation with an older woman named Jaclyn (Jaclyn Taylor), but she also has feelings for her dad's girlfriend, Sarah (Sarah Vandella). When Joey finds out, she decides to teach her sister a lesson.
title: Lesbian Adventures: Older Women, Younger Girls 14
